    "Indeed, the inherent determinism of radar signals is tailored to enhance detection capabilities, while the natural randomness of communication signals is essential to information transmission [29].",
    "This dichotomy presents a unique challenge in integrating the sensing and communication functionalities into a unified system [30].",
    "Thus, facilitating this integration requires careful design of the transceiver [31], transmit waveform [32][33][34][35], signal processing algorithms [10,36], and hardware architecture [37,38] to maintain a good balance between these two functionalities.Fortunately, a lot of effort has been put into the ISAC and different ISAC schemes have been proposed.",
    "According to the functional priorities and the underlying systems, the ISAC schemes can be divided into the following three categories.• Radar-centric scheme.",
